What is it?
We do understand the significance of jewellery
and the important place it holds in all kinds of
festivities or occasions. Be it a diamond ring for
your beloved or a gold bracelet for your kid
jewellery purchase is not only for adornment
purpose but also serves as an investment. So, we
offer an insurance coverage for every purchase
you make from us for 1 year, against any loss or
damage by fire, riot & strike, malicious damage,
burglary, theft, accident, external, or visible means.
By covering the risk, we make sure our customer
is relaxed and will positively keep faith while
making any purchase from us.
How to Claim it?
The claiming procedure is clearly mentioned in the
policy which will be given to you at the time of
purchase. Also in case of any queries, please feel
free to contact us via customer care number 1860
3000 0916 or e-mail us at
care@malabargoldanddiamonds.com.
